::KitKat::

She suddenly felt very tired.  She sat down in wolf mode. "Phobia, 
what can the Vok do?  All I know of them is that they want 
Quickstrike back and used Rowdy for something, but I don't really 
understand them.  Who are they?"

She felt her body start to tingle a little. She was wondering whom to 
trust and who she caouldn't trust.  Drillbit was the only one she 
trusted.  But something in her wanted to listen to Phobia.
